## configmap create 
---
apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: cm
data:
  DB_PORT: "3306"
  DB_USER: admin
  APP_ENV: "dev"


  ### Attach the config to pod

    ---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: pod1
spec:
  containers:
    - name: cont1
      image: kalyanrunval/mobilerepo:mobile
      ports:
        - containerPort: 80
      envFrom:
        - configMapRef:
            name: cm

## configmap lo unna data pod ki attach chesthey aa flie lo unna data antha pod loki velthunde edi non confiedancal data

  To create the env file command -->  kubectl create cm cm2 --from-file=data.env

  
